    "title": "Front Office Manager - Postcard Hotels - Attractive Package",
    "description": "We at Postcard Hotels are looking for an experienced Front Office Manager based out of Bhopal. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Postcard Hotels:\nPostcard Hotels is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Postcard Hotels!",
